1c02ab4fd49ac9","tid":27962,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打用開yanagisawa?<br />\n<br />\n係咪同yamaha差唔多?<br />\n<br />\nTK melody又有咩評價?<br />\n<br />\n利申: alto</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比得起錢買 TK MELODY 不如正經買枝yani。。。<br />\n<br />\n反正 yen 平，飛轉東京大阪自己親手買，好過在香港比人劏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇買過yani，但yani 評級極高。。</blockquote><br />\n因為用開yamaha, 怕yana音色太似<br />\n買2支就浪費左<br />\n<br />\ntk有d 有jazz的音色, 想試下<br />\n相對selmer就平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係勸 各進/高階 巴絲買D 大路嘢好D。。。<br />\n1. H. Selmer Paris<br />\n2. Yanagisawa<br />\n3. Yamaha<br />\n4. Forestone<br />\n5. Julius Keilwerth <br />\nˊ</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTk 我試過好幾支， 個人覺得以現代sax 黎講算好，但如果考慮埋二手價，我會建議買selmer 舊管"},{"pid":"5561b84d30d27f888dcd4a12a872217efbe087b8","tid":27962,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我自己玩左5年幾，頭4年樂器都係借嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年年頭先買左枝yamaha學生型號yas280， 打算之後換專業樂器，師兄又用緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我玩左一年多d, 由細到大既夢想，近年出左黎做野升職加薪先敢開始學。點知一學就上哂癮😛有時發夢都會係度吹👍<br />\n<br />\n我用緊既係ebay bid既selmer balanced action 1938年. D聲甜到漏水😛😛😛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSBA 買幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄，我果支是BA,不是SBA, 比SBA 早一個model"},{"pid":"62d2da0de5cf9db4af181266b6b12d8cf8adb5d3","tid":27962,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"另外我仲有支mk6 tenor😛😛"},{"pid":"cddaaadcc92faeed451d3a3b5486a087a8cd302b","tid":27962,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"學左工聯會幾年之後無學，宜家唔記得曬，有無學校/ 老師推介。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"