016-12-09T00:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收山好耐，我已經唔再敎。。。<br />\n上facebook sax group 找都有好多良師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes, 唔敢係到賣廣告， 不過一支好sax 同一個好老師可以幫你兜少好多路，仲慳唔少錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsax 真係唔好貪平，尤其是報上堂話送sax 嗰尐。尐貨基本上係千鬆D一枝sax，淘記都買到嗰種。 <br />\n<br />\n唔係話淘記嘢一定唔好，但品質參差得好嚴重，初學買中呢尐真係會浪費時間，學壞師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意啊巴打， 上堂送既不如淘寶自己買，佢實有地方賺番你"},{"pid":"80e83f1f50f9a1fd649625f49475ec4ba7e2c66f","tid":27962,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話係男人既浪漫真係冇錯，我發現正常係冇女仔識欣賞</blockquote><br />\n我識喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我反而更欣賞女仔吹sax"},{"pid":"b9c0aa028a2297b13703a93b333031ffd1956cc9","tid":27962,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>另一燒錢行為，有冇alto 吹咀推介</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用緊theo wanne, 好似揸架super car 咁， 踩極都仲有得去， 可以大聲到令自己耳嗚😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控制得好，幾千一隻都覺得值<br />\n至緊要吹得舒服，咀呢家嘢係要慢慢試"},{"pid":"0e41541e7f889a309e2fb1671c836aa545aa3c16","tid":27962,"uid":38261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:49:00.000Z","msg":"想學又一直冇行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f41011ffa584e5ffaf79a4b47a15dd0e353063","tid":27962,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學又一直冇行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平平地去 &ldquo;公賊會&rdquo; 上住 introductory courses，學到咁上吓再找師傅跟吓"},{"pid":"744f3a915ecd8daf1eaa05beecb8414b9ea2fadf","tid":27962,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想學,去邊度學好?<br />\n有巴絲教開saxophone 既可以PM <img src=\"/assets/faces/n